# Task Lifecycle Rule

Todos live in `~/.mission-control/todos/current.md`.

## Format

```markdown
- [ ] [HIGH] Fix auth token refresh loop — TICKET-891 — 2026-07-12
- [ ] [MED] Update AGENTS.md for billing service — 2026-07-12
- [x] [HIGH] Deploy Azure registry hotfix — 2026-07-11
```

## Lifecycle

1. **Add** — `@lu todo add <text>` or write directly. Always include priority and date.
2. **In progress** — change `[ ]` to `[~]` when starting. Lucius will show `[~]` items in status.
3. **Done** — change to `[x]`. Move to `~/.mission-control/todos/done-YYYY-MM.md` weekly.

## Priority guide
- **HIGH** — blocks a mission, team, or deployment
- **MED** — important but not blocking
- **LOW** — nice to have, can wait

## Ticket tagging
Always include the ticket ID if one exists. Format: `PROJ-NNN`

## Lucius integration
- `@lu todo list` — shows all pending + in-progress items
- `@lu status` — shows top 3 high priority todos
